    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎，好奇的心灵和渴望挑战的双手！快进来，快进来，这里在 Labyrintheam，我们的挑战比酒馆的八卦还要曲折，比加热过的汤还要多弯。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果你喜欢考验自己的智慧，那你就来对地方了。我得提醒你，陌生人，仅靠一个坚固的盾牌是远远不够的。不，不……这里需要的是头脑和才智。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个房间都会为你们呈现一个谜题……一扇门，象征着你们的自由。但它不会轻易敞开；你们必须弄清它需要什么技巧来打开通道。或许要找到正确的顺序，或找到合适的符号，甚至像醉酒的巫师的咒语一样，用极其复杂的方式操纵物体。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329520/extras/beaeb8002f8c9b5b9a90f6694b439312.poster.avif?t=1764722196\" width=800 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329520/extras/beaeb8002f8c9b5b9a90f6694b439312.webm?t=1764722196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329520/extras/beaeb8002f8c9b5b9a90f6694b439312.mp4?t=1764722196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我警告你们，陌生人，逻辑和你与伙伴之间的协调就像空气一样必不可少。这是一个需要两人协作的挑战，就像酒和杯，面包和汤一样。仔细观察每个门槛，小心你的每一步，因为一步走错，就如同喝到劣质酒一样危险。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >等待你们的是一个个房间，墙上似乎有眼睛，时钟似乎没有耐心，充满了神秘和惊喜。我保证，它们会让你们甚至怀疑自己的脚步回声。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329520/extras/0c870e758d86b98f21b8dba39ad09887.poster.avif?t=1764722196\" width=800 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329520/extras/0c870e758d86b98f21b8dba39ad09887.webm?t=1764722196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329520/extras/0c870e758d86b98f21b8dba39ad09887.mp4?t=1764722196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所以勇敢前行吧，冒险者们！在 Labyrintheam，你们无法独自逃脱，不，不！这里需要像好伙伴那样齐心协力，否则你们只会变成酒馆的装饰品。记住，只有两颗头脑一起思考，门才会敞开。<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329520/extras/08746a96364fadb432eda0d2b98821ef.poster.avif?t=1764722196\" width=800 height=406 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329520/extras/08746a96364fadb432eda0d2b98821ef.webm?t=1764722196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3329520/extras/08746a96364fadb432eda0d2b98821ef.mp4?t=1764722196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >祝你们好运，陌生人！愿幸运的风总是向你们吹拂！</p>",
